short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Unique JSON viewer in a Text, Tree and Table format. Reads json in <PRE> tag

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
JsonMatrix Extension enable developer and testers to view JSON file in Text, Tree and Table perspective. 
Reads JSON in any webpage with <PRE> tag  and show the JSON in a Tree and Table format.
